On all FIRST CLASS flights drinks and cigarettes are
included in
the service; if available extra supplies of
cigarettes may be purchased during flight.
On TOURIST CLASS services, however, cigarettes and
alcoholic beverages are for sale, at the prices mentioned.
Your cabin attendants will take your order and advise
you on payment in other currencies; they can give you
information about customs regulations, though no
gua-
rantee can be given as to its accuracy, regulations being
subject to alteration at short notice.
Purchases made during flight are not exempt from any
customs duty which may be applicable in the country of
disembarkation.

Op alle EERSTE KLASSE diensten is de verstrekking van
dranken en sigaretten in de passageprijs begrepen; indien
voorradig kunt U bovendien gedurende de vlucht pakjes
sigaretten kopen.
In de TOERISTEN KLASSE kunnen tegen de aangegeven
prijzen, sigaretten en alcoholica worden gekocht bij het
cabinepersoneel,
dat U bovendien over betaling in andere
valuta's kan inlichten.
Aangezien invoerbepalingen dikwijls veranderen, kan men
U daarover aan boord slechts onder voorbehoud inlich-
tingen verstrekken.
Aankopen aan boord ontslaan de passagiers niet van de
douane-voorschriften in het land van ontscheping.
